00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:41,040
I heard in the Prince's yard,

265
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:43,040
there are many jade-colored plum flowers.

266
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:45,570
I haven't had the chance to see them yet.

267
00:16:46,210 --> 00:16:48,990
I just hope that if one day I can see them,

268
00:16:49,220 --> 00:16:51,230
I would be satisifed.

269
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:53,940
If you guys keep on waiting,

270
00:16:55,070 --> 00:16:57,560
you guys might have to wait another seven years.

271
00:16:58,400 --> 00:17:01,410
Alright, today I will make a decision for you guys.

272
00:17:01,940 --> 00:17:04,740
I'll give Huanbi to you.

273
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:05,740
Brother

274
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:07,760
But my position is lowly,

275
00:17:08,270 --> 00:17:10,320
how can I have the privilege of tending to the Prince?

276
00:17:11,040 --> 00:17:13,240
If it wasn't old Seventeen who personally told you

277
00:17:13,940 --> 00:17:15,840
how would you know that he

278
00:17:15,890 --> 00:17:17,610
has jade-colored plum flowers in his yard?

279
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:22,140
And your name is Huanbi (bi meaning jade)

280
00:17:23,150 --> 00:17:26,150
Old Seventeen's household needs a mistress to tend to domestic affairs.

281
00:17:26,900 --> 00:17:30,660
You have always been careful and cautious in your service to Noble Consort Xi.

282
00:17:31,580 --> 00:17:32,870
You,

283
00:17:34,340 --> 00:17:36,440
I have no worries.

284
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:40,740
If you just give Huanbi to the Prince like this,

285
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:42,840
I don't feel it's appropriate either.

286
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:44,540
When she enters the Prince's household,

287
00:17:44,740 --> 00:17:46,140
will her position be escort concubine,

288
00:17:46,340 --> 00:17:48,040
secondary wife, or wife?

289
00:17:48,830 --> 00:17:51,580
Huanbi, as a dowry servant of Noble Consort Xi,

290
00:17:51,820 --> 00:17:53,910
it would be too much to make her even an escort concubine.

291
00:17:59,040 --> 00:18:01,640
Back when I left the palace to meditate,

292
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:04,840
I had only Jinxi and Huanbi by my side.

293
00:18:05,140 --> 00:18:08,640
Huanbi grew up with me and is like a sister to me.

294
00:18:09,620 --> 00:18:12,650
I think, that since the Prince liked Huanbi for seven years,

295
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:15,640
he must not want to treat her lightly.

296
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:18,250
Then what do you want?

297
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:22,540
I want to make Huanbi my godsister,

298
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:24,540
have her name in the genealogy,

299
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:26,440
and as Niuhulu clan's second daughter,

300
00:18:26,940 --> 00:18:29,740
marry proudly into Prince Guojun's household as wife.

301
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:32,440
Noble Consort should know when to stop in sympathizing with Huanbi.

302
00:18:32,740 --> 00:18:34,740
Later when the royal wives enter the palace,

303
00:18:34,940 --> 00:18:36,590
will Huanbi, as the Prince's wife,

304
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:37,840
be sitting equally with us?

305
00:18:38,310 --> 00:18:40,560
I know that Mistress cares for me,

306
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:43,740
but I don't care about positions.

307
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:47,240
Please don't worry for me anymore.

308
00:18:47,540 --> 00:18:48,440
Huanbi,

309
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:50,440
you don't know how messed-up people can be.

310
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:53,410
If you marry without a title into the Prince's house,

311
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:55,240
people will gossip about it.

312
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:58,640
If well-meaning, they will say that you and the Prince have loved each other for a long time

313
00:18:58,740 --> 00:19:00,240
and that this is fate.

314
00:19:00,340 --> 00:19:03,040
If ill-meaning, they might even say you guys were committing adultery (*palace maids weren't allowed to have romantic affairs)

315
00:19:03,540 --> 00:19:05,740
Both of your reputations would be ruined.

316
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:10,140
Brother,

317
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:14,040
forgive me for not marrying Miss Huanbi as my wife.

318
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:16,470
Many years ago,

319
00:19:16,840 --> 00:19:18,540
I met a lady

320
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:19,740
whom I had mutual feelings with.

321
00:19:20,410 --> 00:19:22,060
After, even though we were separated by thousands of miles,

322
00:19:22,060 --> 00:19:23,200
and can't become husband and wife,

323
00:19:23,710 --> 00:19:24,770
but in my heart,

324
00:19:25,290 --> 00:19:27,110
she's my only wife.

325
00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:30,240
Though Miss Huanbi is good,

326
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:33,440
but I will never have her as my wife.

327
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:38,230
I hope that Noble Consort Xi will understand.

328
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:41,440
Emperor should make the decision.

329
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:43,940
Just don't disappoint Huanbi.

330
00:19:43,970 --> 00:19:45,780
I will do as you requested.

331
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:50,940
I will have Huanbi, as the second daughter of the Niuhulu Clan,

332
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:53,640
marry Prince Guojun as the secondary wife.

333
00:19:56,580 --> 00:19:58,410
I thank you Emperor.

334
00:19:58,540 --> 00:20:01,740
Congratulations Prince Guojun! Congratulations Miss Huanbi! <br> Get up!

335
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,240
I salute you.

336
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:44,240
Mistress is drunk.

337
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:47,240
I will take Mistress outside for some fresh air.

338
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:05,940
Huanbi, allow me.

339
00:21:10,140 --> 00:21:11,440
Careful.

340
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:14,240
Careful.

341
00:21:41,840 --> 00:21:43,040
This pair of hands,

342
00:21:44,740 --> 00:21:45,840
this person,

343
00:21:48,140 --> 00:21:50,440
will become Huanbi's from now on.

344
00:21:57,340 --> 00:21:59,340
I know you are upset.

345
00:22:02,740 --> 00:22:04,240
But I'm more upset than you.

346
00:22:12,040 --> 00:22:13,840
Today you celebrate with me,

347
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:19,140
tomorrow you will be my brother-in-law.

348
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,640
Does it have to be this way?

349
00:22:27,140 --> 00:22:28,340
Look,

350
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:33,140
the moon is destined to set in the west.

351
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:40,340
You and I have no other roads to take.

352
00:22:42,840 --> 00:22:44,640
If not this,

353
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:47,240
the dead won't just be you and me.

354
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:50,030
Just rumors,

355
00:22:51,540 --> 00:22:53,840
Wen Shichu is an example.

356
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:56,940
I can't involve you anymore.

357
00:22:58,040 --> 00:22:59,440
That matter from that day,

358
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:03,600
I hate myself for not being able to help you.

359
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:06,740
If it was you who was accused that day,

360
00:23:07,310 --> 00:23:09,060
I would have gone crazy.

361
00:23:15,340 --> 00:23:17,440
Huanbi has always liked you.

362
00:23:20,740 --> 00:23:22,540
Her feelings toward you

363
00:23:23,730 --> 00:23:25,950
are no less than mine.

364
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:29,230
I knew from early on.

365
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:33,370
Don't disappoint her.

366
00:23:38,340 --> 00:23:40,140
You know,

367
00:23:42,140 --> 00:23:45,460
I only want you.

368
00:23:47,840 --> 00:23:50,140
Today will set the boundary between us.

369
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:53,040
Before there was only me.

370
00:23:53,940 --> 00:23:55,540
After there will only be Huanbi.

371
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,940
To tell you the truth

372
00:24:02,340 --> 00:24:04,340
Huanbi isn't my godsister,

373
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:07,240
but my blood sister.

374
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:10,540
Her mother was my father's lover.

375
00:24:11,140 --> 00:24:12,840
But because her father was a criminal,

376
00:24:13,810 --> 00:24:17,010
so father had to hide it

377
00:24:17,940 --> 00:24:20,140
and not let Huanbi be included in the genealogy.

378
00:24:25,090 --> 00:24:26,940
You must treat her well.

379
00:24:50,540 --> 00:24:52,240
The Empress Dowager is very ill.

380
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:54,940
Your marriage will bring happiness to her.

381
00:24:56,470 --> 00:24:59,550
Though the levels of bearing in this marriage don't match,

382
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:02,140
but at least you guys have mutual feelings.

383
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:04,540
I will listen to your arrangements.

384
00:25:04,580 --> 00:25:06,490
On the matter of bearing,

385
00:25:06,540 --> 00:25:09,300
I remember something.

386
00:25:10,140 --> 00:25:11,440
A couple of years ago,

387
00:25:11,740 --> 00:25:14,020
Empress Dowager wanted to arrange a marriage for you.

388
00:25:14,370 --> 00:25:18,770
She was interested in Lord Peiguo's daughter Meng Jingxian.

389
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:22,440
Meng Jingxian met you once when she was young,

390
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,140
and has liked you ever since.

391
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:26,840
Yet you still haven't agreed to it.

392
00:25:27,190 --> 00:25:31,340
That Meng Jingxian became obsessed and refused to marry others.

393
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:35,540
Now she has been delayed and has become an unmarried woman.

394
00:25:35,940 --> 00:25:38,230
The matter of you marrying a secondary wife

395
00:25:38,230 --> 00:25:39,140
has already spread.

396
00:25:39,540 --> 00:25:43,740
Meng Jingxian became very sad

397
00:25:44,780 --> 00:25:46,830
to the extent of being sick in bed.

398
00:25:47,040 --> 00:25:49,640
Lord Peiguo loves his daughter much.

399
00:25:49,790 --> 00:25:52,540
He has already submitted three proposals to me,

400
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:56,640
asking me to understand his daughter's love for you,

401
00:25:56,980 --> 00:26:00,660
and that he would be willing to marry his daughter off

402
00:26:00,740 --> 00:26:03,040
as an escort concubine to serve you.

403
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:06,040
So that he won't lose his daughter in his old age.

404
00:26:06,340 --> 00:26:07,740
You know

405
00:26:07,790 --> 00:26:09,680
that I don't want to marry more than I have to.

406
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:11,740
Besides, I have no feelings for Miss Meng.

407
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:13,280
I don't want to delay her.

408
00:26:13,740 --> 00:26:16,640
Lord Peiguo has been a court official for two Emperors.

409
00:26:17,140 --> 00:26:21,740
Yet his humble speech reflects his deep love for his daughter.

410
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:23,440
I can't help but empathize with him.

411
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:26,820
A man having three or four mistresses

412
00:26:26,820 --> 00:26:28,340
is very normal.

413
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:29,640
I've made up my mind.

414
00:26:30,810 --> 00:26:34,890
Miss Meng and Huanbi will both become your secondary wives.

415
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:36,640
But I've already wasted so many of her years

416
00:26:36,910 --> 00:26:38,800
so I don't want to drag her along for the rest of her life.

417
00:26:38,940 --> 00:26:40,240
Marriage between royals.

418
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:42,840
Being genuine is the least important.

419
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:46,040
I want you to marry her

420
00:26:46,140 --> 00:26:48,040
to reassure the old official.

421
00:26:49,140 --> 00:26:51,640
If you really don't like her

422
00:26:51,740 --> 00:26:53,740
then just care for her at home.

423
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:57,430
Why let her become so ill that she dies?

424
00:26:58,240 --> 00:27:02,240
If Lord Peiguo holds a grudge because of this,

425
00:27:02,700 --> 00:27:06,390
the politics will be chaotic.

426
00:27:06,870 --> 00:27:07,970
With this said,

427
00:27:08,230 --> 00:27:10,310
I just need to care for her

428
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:11,940
and treat her well.

429
00:27:12,540 --> 00:27:14,640
I wanted to hear this.

430
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:15,840
Then I have something to ask.

431
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:17,290
Speak.

432
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:20,740
I ask

433
00:27:21,140 --> 00:27:24,700
to never marry others

434
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:28,350
and I want Huanbi to be in charge of the household.

435
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:34,540
You haven't even married, yet you're showing favoritism.

436
00:27:35,540 --> 00:27:37,840
Miss Meng's health isn't well.

437
00:27:38,030 --> 00:27:40,990
Putting Huanbi in charge of the household is natural.

438
00:27:44,140 --> 00:27:45,440
Marrying secondary wife

439
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:49,230
has clothing obtenance, name choice, marriage fortune report,

440
00:27:49,230 --> 00:27:52,240
dowry obtenance, date choice, and wedding as the six customs.

441
00:27:52,540 --> 00:27:54,960
The rest have been done.

442
00:27:55,150 --> 00:27:56,970
There's only the issue of the name.

443
00:27:57,400 --> 00:28:00,370
As a Niuhulu goddaughter,

444
00:28:00,540 --> 00:28:02,440
my family has the characters "Nu" and "Yu" constituting part of the names for the daughters of this generation.

445
00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:04,440
Huanbi counts as the second miss.

446
00:28:04,840 --> 00:28:06,340
The Internal Affairs Department has prepared

447
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:07,340
a few names starting with Yu.

448
00:28:07,680 --> 00:28:10,810
Huanbi please choose your name.

449
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:14,080
Huanbi, look at them and see

450
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:15,540
which one you like.

451
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:18,740
They're all good names starting with Yu (jade).

452
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:21,630
Yuqin, Yuyin, Yuqiao

453
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,640
Why do they have Yu but have no Nu?

454
00:28:24,940 --> 00:28:26,940
The names don't appear to be for a blood-born Niuhulu daughter.

455
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:30,580
The Customs department said that goddaughters aren't born of the family,

456
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:32,740
and that there must be a distinction.

457
00:28:32,830 --> 00:28:35,350
So only the character Yu will be included in your name.

458
00:28:35,740 --> 00:28:37,040
The doctor said

459
00:28:37,140 --> 00:28:39,030
father's illness has almost fully recovered.

460
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:42,140
Your mother's entrance into our family temple is more important.

461
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:49,160
Then I'll have Yuyin (yin meaning hidden)

462
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:51,340
WIth Niangniang's opinion

463
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:53,250
the dowry, besides the Internal Affairs Department's,

464
00:28:53,340 --> 00:28:55,140
Palace Yongshou will prepare three times as much

465
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:57,440
to give to Miss Yuyin as the dowry?

466
00:28:57,640 --> 00:29:00,140
Consort Jing will oversee the wedding.

467
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:02,240
Zhen household's former servant girl Bin'er

468
00:29:02,340 --> 00:29:04,640
will accompany Miss Yuyin in her marriage.

469
00:29:05,810 --> 00:29:07,520
I won't let your wedding dowry

470
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:09,190
be less than Lord Peiguo's

471
00:29:09,340 --> 00:29:10,640
and become inferior to his daughter in the future.

472
00:29:10,930 --> 00:29:12,480
Thank you Mistress.

473
00:29:13,740 --> 00:29:15,440
The wedding is on June fourth.

474
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:16,790
Niangniang's parents

475
00:29:16,840 --> 00:29:19,340
are being arranged to visit inside the palace.

476
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:32,440
Huaner.

477
00:29:35,540 --> 00:29:37,540
Greetings to father and mother.

478
00:29:37,940 --> 00:29:39,640
Greetins to Noble Consort.

479
00:29:40,630 --> 00:29:42,020
Noble Consort,

480
00:29:42,540 --> 00:29:44,940
You can't perform the great bow to us!

481
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:48,240
I am not filial,

482
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:50,620
Carrying Niuhulu's last name,

483
00:29:50,940 --> 00:29:53,140
I couldn't meet you at Yongshou palace.

484
00:29:53,140 --> 00:29:56,290
As long as we reunite as a family

485
00:29:56,340 --> 00:29:58,240
it is the same wherever we go.

486
00:29:58,940 --> 00:30:00,040
Let's get up.

487
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,740
Get up.

488
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:04,140
Get up.

489
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:07,240
Come, sit.

490
00:30:15,940 --> 00:30:17,540
In all these years

491
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:20,590
mother has grown many white hairs.

492
00:30:24,540 --> 00:30:26,240
We've endured all these years.

493
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:29,640
And now we've gotten out of it.

494
00:30:31,090 --> 00:30:33,380
Back when our family was in decline,

495
00:30:33,730 --> 00:30:36,170
I was just afraid that it would trouble you too.

496
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:39,540
We're a family. Don't speak of troubling each other.

497
00:30:40,740 --> 00:30:42,640
Now it's all better

498
00:30:42,760 --> 00:30:44,660
and Yuying is getting married.

499
00:30:45,630 --> 00:30:48,660
Yuying having this fate

500
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:51,120
her mother,

501
00:30:52,390 --> 00:30:57,270
can rest in peace now.

502
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,540
Although it's secondary wife,

503
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:03,840
but Yuying sincerely likes the lord.

504
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:06,940
Her wish has been granted.

505
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:09,840
This is all to your trouble.

506
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:11,940
You have worried much for her.

507
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:17,740
Parents living at an inn

508
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:20,140
is not a long term solution.

509
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:25,280
The Emperor has people fixing up Zhen estate.

510
00:31:25,970 --> 00:31:29,430
Mother and father can live peacefully.

511
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:38,200
His Majesty allowing us to visit you in the palace

512
00:31:38,270 --> 00:31:40,720
is already a huge gift of kindness.

513
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:43,820
How can we ask to live in this city for such a long time?

514
00:31:44,940 --> 00:31:47,940
Being able to see you and the grandchild is satisfying.

515
00:31:48,340 --> 00:31:50,840
I am much comforted.

516
00:31:50,940 --> 00:31:53,040
I don't ask for anything else.

517
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:55,540
Since you've returned,

518
00:31:56,140 --> 00:31:57,340
I won't let you

519
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:59,140
return to the poor mountains.

520
00:32:00,740 --> 00:32:02,040
Using this return

521
00:32:02,230 --> 00:32:04,480
I will find a way to ask the Emperor

522
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:06,640
to investigate that year's events.

523
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:12,140
Originally

524
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:14,340
Second Miss has always worn jade-colored clothing.

525
00:32:14,340 --> 00:32:18,040
Who would have thought that you wearing red is even prettier?

526
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:22,240
It's a pity that it's only secondary wife,

527
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:24,640
and I can't wear true red.

528
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:32,940
Very beautiful, so pretty.

529
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:37,340
Thank you, older sister, for arranging all of this.

