00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:51,690
but you also must not nitpick on everything.

535
00:32:51,840 --> 00:32:53,640
Live a peaceful life.

536
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:55,140
The lord said

537
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:58,000
that you will be in charge of everything at his estate.

538
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:59,940
Balance justice and mercy.

539
00:33:00,340 --> 00:33:02,140
The upper and lower households must be treated appropriately.

540
00:33:02,980 --> 00:33:05,180
Sister, I'm sorry.

541
00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:08,140
This position should have been yours.

542
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:10,640
I took your position.

543
00:33:11,830 --> 00:33:14,520
My position is the Emperor's Noble Consort Xi.

544
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:16,640
How did you take mine?

545
00:33:18,050 --> 00:33:19,970
Tomorrow you are to wed.

546
00:33:20,050 --> 00:33:21,800
You need to be very happy.

547
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,180
Don't think too much about other things.

548
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,740
Sister.

549
00:33:25,430 --> 00:33:27,500
I know you are sad.

550
00:33:29,630 --> 00:33:31,920
The bride needs to be happy,

551
00:33:32,670 --> 00:33:34,500
how can you cry?

552
00:33:34,540 --> 00:33:36,240
Sister, do you regret it?

553
00:33:37,320 --> 00:33:38,610
That year

554
00:33:39,140 --> 00:33:40,840
if you waited a few more months

555
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:43,940
today the person marrying the lord

556
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:46,640
wouldn't be me.

557
00:33:48,250 --> 00:33:49,960
I chose my own path

558
00:33:51,340 --> 00:33:54,240
so there's no going back.

559
00:33:55,540 --> 00:33:57,740
Living in the palace is too difficult.

560
00:33:58,140 --> 00:34:01,440
I don't have the time, or mood to regret anything.

561
00:34:02,300 --> 00:34:06,100
Your future path has been determined by your choice today.

562
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:07,930
I hope that

563
00:34:07,930 --> 00:34:10,040
you can always move on with out regretting anything.

564
00:34:11,210 --> 00:34:12,430
Sister I'm afraid.

565
00:34:12,660 --> 00:34:16,240
I am worried that the lord's heart will only have you.

566
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:17,890
I don't know

567
00:34:17,890 --> 00:34:19,740
how to be this secondary wife.

568
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:24,740
For your matter, I am an outsider.

569
00:34:25,590 --> 00:34:28,590
Prince Guojun household's husband is you and the prince.

570
00:34:29,450 --> 00:34:32,700
How to accomplish this is all up to you.

571
00:34:32,940 --> 00:34:36,340
I can only tell you to be genuine.

572
00:34:36,690 --> 00:34:38,820
Being genuine is the most important.

573
00:34:40,340 --> 00:34:41,540
Sister

574
00:34:42,140 --> 00:34:44,840
I will use all of my heart to treat the lord well.

575
00:34:45,700 --> 00:34:47,540
I will be filial to his mother.

576
00:34:48,870 --> 00:34:50,620
You just need to remember

577
00:34:50,740 --> 00:34:52,740
that from now on, on our shoulders

578
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:54,840
we carry the Zhen family's future.

579
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,340
Remember.

580
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:59,840
You are the lord's secondary wife.

581
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:23,640
Niuhulu Yuyin bids farewell to Noble Consort Xi.

582
00:35:25,980 --> 00:35:27,830
Take care of yourself.

583
00:35:43,110 --> 00:35:45,680
The lucky time has come, and the lord's estate is ready.

584
00:35:45,740 --> 00:35:47,340
Lord Peiguo's is already on their way.

585
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:48,950
Second miss may leave now.

586
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:51,210
Go.

587
00:36:07,010 --> 00:36:08,590
I'd rather it was you.

588
00:36:10,740 --> 00:36:13,440
That way he'd be happy.

589
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:20,940
Yuying has more fortune than I do.

590
00:36:27,100 --> 00:36:28,720
Marrying two at once.

591
00:36:30,140 --> 00:36:32,440
But both are not the ones he wants.

592
00:36:34,340 --> 00:36:36,440
Raise the sedan.

593
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:52,740
Time's mistiming has never stopped.

594
00:36:53,240 --> 00:36:54,540
It's normal.

595
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:32,640
Congratulations!

596
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,940
Congratulations Lord Guojing!

597
00:37:37,240 --> 00:37:39,340
Come, let's drink!

598
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:41,440
So lucky!

599
00:37:41,540 --> 00:37:42,640
Two secondary wives.

600
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:44,340
Right, congratulations.

601
00:37:44,840 --> 00:37:46,440
Congratulations!

602
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:49,640
Happy!

603
00:37:50,140 --> 00:37:52,040
Congratulations!

604
00:38:17,540 --> 00:38:19,240
Lord, lord.

605
00:38:19,640 --> 00:38:20,640
Come, get up.

606
00:38:20,940 --> 00:38:22,040
Don't touch me.

607
00:38:22,440 --> 00:38:23,840
I'm fine.

608
00:38:28,350 --> 00:38:29,390
I'm fine.

609
00:38:30,540 --> 00:38:33,240
Lord, two secondary wives, you need to say something.

610
00:38:33,340 --> 00:38:35,040
Who's place are you going to sleep tonight?

611
00:38:38,040 --> 00:38:39,640
Lord, it's your big night.

612
00:38:39,670 --> 00:38:41,990
You can't just not go to any of them.

613
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:45,940
Lord. Lord!

614
00:38:46,680 --> 00:38:48,590
Huan...Huanbi.

615
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:50,730
Okay. To Changqing Ge!

616
00:38:53,340 --> 00:38:54,340
Lord.

617
00:38:54,430 --> 00:38:56,360
Miss, it's time to sleep.

